[b=1000][left][s=25][u]
line>Plasma Structure Text (PST)<
[/b][left][s=16][/u]
text>Plasma Structure Text (PST) is a markup language designed for structuring and formatting content within the PlasmaNet ecosystem. It is used to define the presentation of text and hyperlinks in a simple and readable format.<
[i][b=1000]
text> PST<
[/i][/b]
text> is optimized for ease of use and flexibility, allowing content creators to focus on the content itself rather than complex syntax.<
line><
[i][center][s=20][u]
line>Key Features:<
[/i][/u][left]
line><
[font=Courier][s=16]
line>- [b] and [/b]: Bold text with weight. e.g., [b=1000]<
line>- [i] and [/i]: Italicize text.<
line>- [u] and [/u]: Underline text.<
line>- [s=size] and [/s]: Set font size, e.g., [s=25] for size 25.<
line>- [font=fontname]: Set font family, e.g., [font=Arial].<
line>- [center], [left], [right]: Align text to the center, left, or right.<
line>- line>< and text><: Define line breaks and plain text.<
line>- link<url>text<: Create clickable hyperlinks.<
line><
[i][center][s=20][u]
line>Example Usage:<
[/i][/u][left]
line><

[left][s=16][u]
line>How to Create a Bold, Underlined Header:<
[/u]
[font=Courier][s=16]
line>[b=1000][left][s=25][u]<<
line>line>Welcome to PlasmaNet!<<
line>[/b][left][s=16][/u]<<
line><

[left][s=16][u]
line>How to Use Links:<
[/u]
[font=Courier][s=16]
line>link<pttp://main.com/learn_more>Learn More<<
line><

[left][s=16][u]
line>Centered Important Notice (EXAMPLE):<
[/u]
